node_7.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_7.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, open Hobbs Cafe at 8:00 am and work at the counter until 8:00 pm. This includes managing staff, preparing meals and interacting with customers. She also spends some time checking inventory and ordering supplies for the cafe, Starting at 4:00 pm, Isabella starts preparations for the Valentine's Day party tomorrow. This includes decorating the cafe, finalizing the menu, and promoting the event on social media and with her customers, Around 7:00 pm, Isabella takes a short break to eat dinner, At 8:00 pm, she closes the cafe and cleans up for the night.
